Build instructions:
-------------------

Prequisites:

   - qt 4.3.3 (or newer)
   - tetlib 1.4.2 (or newer)
   - nglib 4.5 (or newer)

Please read the file LICENSES before using any of these software packages.

Build as follows:

   $ qmake -project

Edit "Mesh3D.pro" and add the following lines somewhere in the file:

   QT += opengl
   LIBS += -ltet -lng

   $ qmake
   $ make

This should produce the executable "./release/Mesh3D".
